---
title: Honey-Soy Chicken Salad with Roasted Pumpkin & Peanuts
description: Make space for this hearty salad in your dinner rotation. With mildly spiced chicken and crunchy peanuts, this plate of bountiful greens and pumpkin will change the way you look at veggies!

*Unfortunately, this week's cucumber and courgette were in short supply, so we've replaced them with pear and capsicum. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-soy-chicken-salad-80f3155e.jpg
